OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FThe government has announced radical
OL,7,Freforms to the UK's asylum system,
OL,8,Flaunching a package of changes which
OL,9,Fthey call the biggest in "modern
OL,10,Fhistory".
OL,12,FAnnouncing the plans on Monday, the PM
OL,13,Fsaid the changes were required to cope
OL,14,Fwith a more "volatile and insecure"
OL,15,Fworld.
OL,17,FStarmer said there was now a "severe
OL,18,Fstrain on both our asylum system and
OL,19,Four wider social contract".
