OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FThe changes are aimed at reducing the
OL,7,F"pull factors" that make people want
OL,8,Fto come to the UK, by making it harder
OL,9,Fto get permanent refugee status,
OL,10,Freducing barriers to deportation and
OL,11,Freforming human rights laws.
OL,13,FStarmer insisted "the UK is a decent,
OL,14,Fcompassionate, tolerant country that
OL,15,Fcelebrates diversity."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
