OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FLonger waits for UK citizenship
OL,8,FUnder the current rules, if an asylum
OL,9,Fseeker's claim is approved they then
OL,10,Fget refugee status for five years
OL,11,Fbefore they can apply for indefinite
OL,12,Fleave to remain (ILR).
OL,14,FA year after getting ILR, they can
OL,15,Fthen apply for British citizenship.
OL,17,FBut under the new plans, refugees will
OL,18,Fhave to wait 20 years before they can
OL,19,Fget permanent settlement.
