OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FUnder the new plans asylum seekers
OL,7,Fcould also lose the automatic right to
OL,8,Fsome benefits and housing help, with
OL,9,Fthe legal duty to provide support
OL,10,Frevoked and instead made
OL,11,F"discretionary". The government say
OL,12,Fthis will happen in the "coming
OL,13,Fmonths".
OL,15,FThe small proportion of asylum seekers
OL,16,Fwho have a right to work will have
OL,17,Ftheir support removed, and those with
OL,18,Fassets will also lose automatic access
OL,19,Fto support, along with individuals who
OL,20,Fdo not comply with the law.
