OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FThe legal duty to provide support to
OL,7,Fasylum seekers was introduced in the
OL,8,FUK in 2005 under EU law, it entitles
OL,9,Fasylum seekers to somewhere to live,
OL,10,Fand a weekly payment of #49.18, or
OL,11,F#9.95 if the accommodation provides
OL,12,Ffood.
OL,14,FThe government will also consult on
OL,15,Fchanges to the benefits system to
OL,16,Fprioritise access for people making
OL,17,F"an economic contribution" to the UK.
