OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FThe government has been saying for
OL,7,Fsome time that they want to reform the
OL,8,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights
OL,9,F(ECHR), focusing on article 3 which
OL,10,Fprovides protection from torture or
OL,11,Finhumane treatment, and article 8
OL,12,Fwhich guarantees the right to family
OL,13,Flife.
OL,15,FMahmood will bring forward a bill to
OL,16,Fchange how article 8 is applied in
OL,17,Fmigration court cases, and also plans
OL,18,Fto change the law so that multiple
OL,19,Fattempts to appeal against rejected
OL,20,Fasylum claims will no longer be
OL,21,Fallowed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
