OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FThere has been a significant rise in
OL,7,Frecent years of rights-based appeals
OL,8,Fas a means of avoiding deportation,
OL,9,Fincluding by some serious criminals.
OL,11,FUnder the new rules, only those with
OL,12,Fimmediate family in the UK will be
OL,13,Fable to use article 8 as grounds to
OL,14,Fstay.
OL,16,FA new independent body will also be
OL,17,Fset up to fast-track the removal of
OL,18,Fdangerous criminals, and late appeals
OL,19,Fwill be expedited.
