OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FThe government has announced it will
OL,7,Fbring in Trump-style visa sanctions
OL,8,Ffor countries who fail to take back
OL,9,Fillegal migrants.
OL,11,FInitially, three African countries
OL,12,Fwill be targeted ` Angola, Namibia and
OL,13,Fthe Democratic Republic of Congo ` if
OL,14,Fthey do not co-operate more on the
OL,15,Fremoval of illegal migrants.
OL,17,FThey'll face visa sanctions, and their
OL,18,Ftourists, VIPs and business people
OL,19,Fcould be blocked from travelling to
OL,20,FBritain, under plans reportedly
OL,21,Finspired by Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
