OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FMahmood is focusing particularly on
OL,7,Fremoving families - the government
OL,8,Fargues some asylum seekers in the UK
OL,9,F"exploit the fact that they have had
OL,10,Fchildren and put down roots in order
OL,11,Fto thwart removal".
OL,13,FThe government says its "hesitance
OL,14,Faround returning families" has created
OL,15,F"perverse incentives" to put children
OL,16,Fon small boats.
OL,18,FUnder the new plans, families will be
OL,19,Foffered financial support to encourage
OL,20,Fthem to go home, but if they refuse
OL,21,Fthey will be forced to return.
