OL,3,CEverything you need to know about the
OL,4,Cgovernment's asylum shake-up
OL,6,FThe government says "we will not seize
OL,7,Fitems of jewellery at the border",
OL,8,Fdespite reports that the overhaul
OL,9,Fcould include plans to confiscate
OL,10,Fwatches and jewellery in an idea
OL,11,Fborrowed from Denmark.
OL,13,FThe Home Office insist family
OL,14,Fheirlooms and jewellery won't be
OL,15,Ftaken, but high value items like cars
OL,16,Fand e-scooters could be seized to
OL,17,Fcontribute to the cost of
OL,18,Faccommodation.
OL,20,FThe Liberal Democrats have called the
OL,21,Fplans "state-endorsed robbery."
