OL,6,FBut minister Alex Norris urged
OL,7,Fbackbenchers to look "closely" at the
OL,8,Fpolicy when it's announced in the
OL,9,FCommons.
OL,11,FWhat do opposition parties and
OL,12,Fcharities say?
OL,14,FThe Conservatives welcomed some of the
OL,15,Fmeasures, but warn that "some are just
OL,16,Fyet more gimmicks".
OL,18,FThe party has offered to support the
OL,19,Fgovernment to get the changes through,
OL,20,Fespecially if it races a rebellion
OL,21,Ffrom Labour backbenchers.
