OL,6,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage told the
OL,7,FDaily Mail that Mahmood "sounds like a
OL,8,FReform supporter".
OL,10,FEnver Solomon, chief executive at the
OL,11,FRefugee Council, meanwhile described
OL,12,Fthe government's plans as "harsh and
OL,13,Funnecessary", and claimed they "won't
OL,14,Fdeter people who have been persecuted,
OL,15,Ftortured or seen family members killed
OL,16,Fin brutal wars".
OL,18,FHe added: "Instead, they are more
OL,19,Flikely to force them into destitution
OL,20,Fand sleeping rough on the streets."
